### ESPC25 Local LLM Chat API - HTTP Test File
### Base URL: https://localhost:7154

# Note: Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with actual JWT token from Azure AD

### Get all chat sessions
GET https://localhost:7154/api/chat/sessions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Create a new chat session
POST https://localhost:7154/api/chat/sessions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Test Chat Session"
}

### Get a specific chat session
GET https://localhost:7154/api/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Send a message to a chat session (text only)
POST https://localhost:7154/api/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Hello, how are you today?
--boundary123--

### Send a message with file attachment
POST https://localhost:7154/api/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Can you analyze this document for me?
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./path/to/your/document.pdf
--boundary123--

### Get an attachment
GET https://localhost:7154/api/chat/attachments/{{attachmentId}}
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get weather forecast (demo endpoint)
GET https://localhost:7154/WeatherForecast

